name: 'Windrunner' Colorblock Jacket
description: This bold color-blocked running jacket of tough ripstop fabric is framed by banded trim for a distraction-free fit and topped by an adjustable hood for extra coverage. The lightweight design features a ventilating back yoke and breathable mesh lining so you don't overheat from warm-up to cool-down.
